title: SPY 2013/14 SNOW PK - BIAS
description:
THE SLEEK-PROFILE BIAS IS SPECIFICALLY DESIGNED FOR SMALLER FACES WITH ELEGANT DESIGN DETAILS, A SMART PINSTRIPE AND FRESH METALLIC ACCENTS. 

THE BIAS FEATURES A FLEXIBLE FRAME DESIGNED FOR SMALLER FACES, PATENTED SCOOP® VENTING SYSTEM TO COMBAT LENS FOGGING, 6-BASE ARC® SPHERICAL DUAL LENS SYSTEM WITH ANTI-FOG & ANTI-SCRATCH PROTECTION, TRIPLE LAYER ISOTRON™ FACE FOAM FEATURING MOISTURE-WICKING DRI-FORCE™ FLEECE, PIVOTING STRAP-CLIP SYSTEM ENSURING A COMFORTABLE FIT, WITH OR WITHOUT A HELMET, DUAL-ADJUSTMENT, SILICONE-RIBBED STRAP WITH QUICK-RELEASE STRAP BUCKLE, 100% UV PROTECTION, AND IS HELMET COMPATIBLE.
